name: 05.Predictive Analysis
content:
Predictive Analysis and Insights

  • Top 5 High-Risk Cities – Locations most likely to have BTS deployment issues.
  • Top 5 Low-Risk Cities – Safest locations for deployment with minimal risk.
  • Feature Impact Analysis – How audit, financial, and past performance influence deployment risk.
  • Deployment Dashboard:
  • Number of BTS installations per city.
  • Regions flagged for risk.
  • Model predictions integrated with business decision-making.
